Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好滴，下一个应用我们要一起\NOkay, so the next app that we're going to build together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,编写一个非常简单的天气应用\Nis a very simple weather application.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到 Windows 10 的 PC 和手机都自带了\NNow I realize there are stock apps that come with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很多常用的应用\NWindows 10 on the desktop and the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个应用可以让我们表达\Nhowever, this one will allow us to express
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一点特色和设计感\Na little individuality, a little design.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,另外我还要演示一些\NAlso, we'll demonstrate some pretty cool features
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在 Windows 10 多平台间非常有趣的特性\Nof both Windows 10 the platform
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,以及如何从外部服务中获得\Nand then how to work with external services
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,实时的数据，从而让你的应用变得实时\Nto get data to update and make your apps come alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好，首先让我们先运行一下这个 App\NSo I'll go ahead and run the application.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,让我先运行一下它的桌面版\NActually let me run it just on the desktop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但相信我它在手机上\Nand just have to trust me that it works
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也能跑得起来\Nin the mobile version as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个应用我给它赐名为:\NAnd the name of the application I'm calling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,UWP 天气 (●'◡'●)\NUWP Weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个简单的天气应用\NIt's a simple weather app.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,它会基于当前我在达拉斯的实际位置\NIt's just going to go out and based on my current location
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后去找出我所处位置的实时天气\Nhere in Dallas, it's going to go out and find the current weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,像天气情况如何，具体的地理位置在哪\Nwhat the weather conditions are, where I'm actually at here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在所处 普莱诺，德克萨斯州。 它还会展示一个\NI'm in Plano, Texas and then also will display
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在粉色背景下可爱的天气图片\Nan image, a cute weather image with a hot pink background
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,图片显示我所在地方的实时天气\Nto convey what the current weather is where I'm at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在编写这个 App 中\NSo in the process of building this, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是一个非常好的开始\Nthis is a great start to a weather application
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你编写这个应用并去扩充它，学习\Nthat you can take and extend and you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如何去它的功能\Nto learn how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以添加，比如，使用在线服务\NYou can add, you know, a two week forecast if you want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,提供提前两周的天气预报，具体服务稍后就说\Nusing online services that I'll point you to in this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你将要学到一件重要的事情\NBut one of the main things that you'll learn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是如何利用你 Windows 10 设备上的传感器\Nis how to use sensors on your device or in actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,或者定位服务来定位你手机\Nthe location services for Windows 10 to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,或者电脑的地理位置，\Nthe geo position where the device or your computer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,从中获得的经纬度数据\Nis currently at So that would give the latitude
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用来\Nand longitude that we can then take
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,调用外部的天气 Web 服务\Nand we can make calls out to an external web service
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,比如 OpenWeatherMap.org 这个网站\Nlike the OpenWeatherMap.org,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它允许我们提交一个地方的经度和维度\Nwhich will allow us to give in a place,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后获得那个地方的天气\Na latitude, longitude, will give us the weather
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至有几小时后、几天后\Nfor that location and even future forecasts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,的天气预告\Nfor the hours and days ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从中我们将学习\NSo it's going to also allow us then
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如何从 Web 服务中获取数据\Nto learn how to retrieve data from a web service
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,使用一种典型的数据格式化样式\Nin a typical fashion through a file format
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做 JSON (JavaScript 对象表述方法) \Ncalled JSON (JavaScript Object Notation),
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你早就熟悉它\Nmaybe you're already familiar with that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,知道使用 C# 将它反序列化成\Nand deserialize that into instances of classes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,类实例\Nthat we can work with in C#.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个非常有用的技能，抛开这个例子\NVery crucial skill, outside of this example
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个开发者，学会它\Nand throughout the rest of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你将终身受益\Nas a software developer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须知道对于一些数据格式\NYou have to know how to serialize and desterialize data
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,像 XML，JSON，如何序列化和反序列化数据\Nfrom data formats like XML and JSON
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最终实现来回转换\Ninto objects and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们还要看看如何使用\NAnd then we're going to look at how to work with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,手机模拟器来测试我们的应用\Nthe Phone Emulator to test our application,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是测试一些转到手机上运行的部分\Nnot just as it's used on the mobile device itself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,像是布局，一些性质\Nand the layout, things of that nature, but then also
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要学会如何去修改位置\Nhow to change the position
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,例如告诉位置服务\Nand kind of tell the location services
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在在西雅图或者华盛顿\Nthat we're actually coming from, Seattle or Washington, DC,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至天朝，等等\Nor China, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要来看一下在使用手机测试时\NAnd so we'll look at a cool feature of the emulator
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一项非常酷炫的特性\Nto do that as well for testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,之后将为我们的应用创建\NAnd then we're going to take a look at how to build
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一个活动磁贴\Na Live Tile for our application
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还将定期地使用地理位置和经纬度\Nthat we'll update periodically with the latest weather
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来获取最新的天气\Nfor our geo position, our latitude and longitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,从中我们不仅学到如何来创建一个活动磁贴\NAnd so that will teach us not only how to build live tiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而且包括了如何创建一个 Web 服务\Nbut then also we'll learn how to create a web service
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,使用ASP.NET MVC 5，从自己的主机来运行这个服务\Nusing ASP.NET MVC 5 and host it out as your website
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们集合了相当多有趣的技术来\Nso we're bring together a lot of cool technologies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,构建一个富交互的应用\Nto build a very interactive application.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,下节课，我们将确定布局\NSo beginning in the next video we'll get started
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,学习如何去接入一个 Web 服务\Nwith the layout and learning how to access that web service
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,从中获取我们需要的数据\Nand get back the data that we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那下节课我们正式开始\NWe'll begin that process in the next video.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候见，再见\NWe'll see you there, thanks.
